Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:39.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么美妙的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  崇子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  这不才四点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.70,0:01:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The early bird catches the worm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.66,0:01:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们身负喜翠庄的日常业务
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着还要准备我们的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了完成这繁重的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.61,0:02:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只能从削减年轻人的睡眠时间开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:14.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之  接下来要和anything开一场会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发去员工食堂  Here we go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊  崇子小姐突然好有干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good moring Miss巴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始这美妙的一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来  Miss巴请就座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来开始会议
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要拿出干劲来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  芥川龙之介写这部「罗生门」的经过是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时芥川和他的青梅竹马  吉田弥生的婚约告吹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它很少会响的所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  男朋友怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要说男女朋友什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想什么呀  真难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在上课的时候打电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得你是不是一直都在干活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是个女高中生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我收到了张请帖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缘他要结婚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定会参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那么容易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  工作很忙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.58,0:03:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  各种原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贺电的话我会发一个的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来缘结婚了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被他超前了呢  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  妈妈你一直在换男朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟别人交往到底是种什么感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？  你又把上其他男人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:24.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没准还对你爸爸单相思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单相思？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这算什么口气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家还以为说了一句不错的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.30,0:04:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是单相思这个词
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本想不到会从放荡的妈妈嘴里说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为忘不了喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才摸索其他恋情的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让这份感情又得不到回报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那人去世至今也有十五年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我会开始这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也没有必要得到回报了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少能遇到让自己喜欢到这种地步的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是遇到  就已经足够幸运了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  绪花？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.74,0:05:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然为妈妈的单相思心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  单相思…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…为什么我会想要放弃阿孝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连小民都能那么认真地对彻先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会想不到这是单相思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好咧  完成了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一个外行而言做得挺不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是试穿  再做做微调了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名同学穿穿看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种说法是穿上婚纱婚期就会延后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我穿的话  下摆肯定要拖地的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉之前貌似也有过一次这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种怪讨厌的既视感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.11,0:06:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已  已经可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴小姐正在努力地做我们那份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么让鹤来同学穿穿看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那边没准还不如崇子小姐有料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没胸反而方便试穿不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之没胸走遍天下都不怕  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.47,0:07:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来你就要开始试做宴会料理了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我基本上都有点底了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个…我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.09,0:07:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过用不着帮忙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.92,0:07:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  我已经放弃胡萝卜政策了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有严苛的环境  人是无法摆脱低潮的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于想通了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要像当时冷酷无情的莲先生那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷酷…无情？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民好迟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.09,0:08:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是大家一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最后的调整还…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不穿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种轻飘飘的衣服我绝对不穿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可  可是…小民…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等  小民！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我不爽这没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.06,0:08:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那件婚纱是我和小菜还有结名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.81,0:08:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了少爷和崇子小姐才做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做得非常用心！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却把那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少啰嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你非常用心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道彻先生就不是了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你践踏了非常用心的彻先生的心意！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻  彻先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我决定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要单恋阿孝！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像小民这样直接
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:08:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡说八道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少给我去搞什么单相思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去跟彻先生交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死  去死  去死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  要是死了就没法交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我已经决定要单恋阿孝了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝什么的那种傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.17,0:09:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民你又没见过他！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟彻先生相比  男人全都是傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}小民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.63,0:09:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生他那么有型！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那么出色！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再吵了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民  等一等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嘛…那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实对绪花有点意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定…真是有点喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不是说我就要怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是看到她时会有些兴奋而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会去猜测她接下来又会做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看到你时我会放不下心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我刚说了什么过分的话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算彻先生并不喜欢我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一样会关注我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  基本都弄干净了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.47,0:11:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.89,0:11:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我还没谈过恋爱什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得这一定很美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美妙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一直单相思下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然吵架是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我觉得绪花和小民都很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.99,0:11:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像那样思念着一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被你们感动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么感动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常合适
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  试着拿些白色鲜花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来有在电视上看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会显得华贵一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把楼梯旁边的花拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻子不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的必须要和彻先生交往吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:12:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我想和彻先生交往
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是这个不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要交往  所以会继续单相思的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直冲目标  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花…又吵架…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛蛋复活祭哟～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后  婚礼的准备也顺利进行着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉中我下定了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚礼顺利结束后就去告白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  挺不错的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是无微不至
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  多亏了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚礼一定会顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民  这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐  好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.60,0:14:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是女人一生中最漂亮的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人一生中…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛花团的时候一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学毕业后好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候和崇子好上的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们就此成为夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能向大家宣布这件事情我非常感动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.48,0:15:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在大家面前发誓   从今天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们夫妻将互相帮助  互相分享
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,营造一个幸福的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开场结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是和时间赛跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.21,0:15:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司仪什么的  好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  押水同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名的头发没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不奇怪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不奇怪  待会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗中的押水同学  真新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房如战场  开工了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻  发号施令吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你是这里的主厨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  莲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那里的蔬菜处理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把鲤鱼的鳞片刮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有把天妇罗油炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后把黄瓜雕花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真过分啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.27,0:16:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此由我诵读一下贺电
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是新郎的姐姐  松前皋月发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗话说雨后土固
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}注：形容经历挫折之后现状会变得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.79,0:16:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说不知今天天气如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.90,0:17:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之坚固是件好事  缘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对男人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一道料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才就是最后一道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.52,0:17:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请柬？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场婚礼  我们也被邀请了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都好美味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  还是第一次好好品尝彻先生的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.10,0:17:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我没能阻止…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  下一个节目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我的命中注定的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的  崇子小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.09,0:18:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那边在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  爱的Baiser
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}（Baiser：法语  接吻）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘  有反应就输了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的婚礼  我完全没有插手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  这里的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及喜翠庄工作的年轻人们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举办了如此成功的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提下我的往事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40年前  我和已逝的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有在这里的电六
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.65,0:19:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  和电六先生三人一起建起了喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕受挫  迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会毫不畏惧挑战未知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造新的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位以及大家一起创造的新的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就满怀期待  在远处喝着粗茶守望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:20.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守望？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.22,0:22:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺利…结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快收拾完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才老板娘所说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让大家都聚在这里不为别的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.33,0:22:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前电六先生和我谈过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.55,0:22:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.05,0:22:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电六先生他说了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40年间不曾间断记录着的工作日记
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该让谁来继承了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆丁老爷  就是说要离开喜翠庄了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  豆丁老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.85,0:23:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份工作日记就是喜翠庄的历史本身
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪和欢笑全都记录于此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.73,0:23:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得如此破烂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.65,0:23:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄将在这次的雪洞祭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.11,0:23:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与日记一同结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}要去见他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}单相思的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.36,0:23:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耐心的等待也是男人的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.67,0:23:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花 你才不是什么没味的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
